---
title: Thyme & Rosemary Crusted Chicken with Creamy Potato & Green Bean Salad
description: This weeknight wonder of herb-crusted chicken tastes just like classic chicken and stuffing, in less than half the time. Served with a potato salad, this will quickly turn into a favourite dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c108a16c445fa556d731be3-a507c8dc.jpg
